TWO sold out shows. In love with these guys. I’ve never  felt more loved and protected than I do now. As a young woman in my 20’s I always dreamed of working in an environment where an equal love and respect was shared. I never imagined it would happen. Grateful to the universe for providing. I’m not sure that I deserve you all, but I’m going to enjoy this moment. Truly humbled and grateful to share the stage and the success of this band with all of you. 📸 @piperferguson 📸 @kingrockphoto
More star shots from @kingrockphoto . Thank you.

One year.

One year of trying
One year of falling and getting back up
One year of hoping
One year of believing
One year of feeling
One year of doing
One year of losing
One year of finding.
One year of mourning.
One year of recovery. 
One year of loving and being loved
One year of letting go.
One year of forgiving. 

I miss my mom. But I’m happy to have had the time I did with her. I miss my parents, but today I do what I do with new purpose and meaning. I do it for them. 

This has been a year of healing.
Today I feel reborn in a way.
I can say the pain has been worth it.
Today I’m happy to be alive.

Shame on you, @volaris_airlines_rblx @flyvolaris @viajavolaris  for allowing us to book flights weeks prior, leave us with the impression our flights were secure on booking, then blame us for your @americanexpress processing issues after not informing us, making us pay for upgrades for telephone assistance (who pays EXTRA to get someone on the phone?) tell us over three phone calls the morning of the flight that our reservation is secure, then have Kenny at ticketing at @flylaxairport tell us we have no flights. Kenny then made us fight with him for OVER TWO hours (yes we were three hours early for our flight which was already delayed two hours) to let us on the flight we had rightfully paid for. The same flight Kenny the gaslight king told us was FULL. Shame on you for making us pay you over ONE THOUSAND DOLLARS IN CASH to get on a flight that was reserved and paid for three weeks prior. And then forcing us to leave one member behind to find a different flight. In all our collective years of travel, hundreds of flights to everywhere in the world, collectively, not one of us have experienced something like this. For the lies, abuse, and for the extortion, for your crooked business practices we ask our fans to #boycottvolaris see you all in Mexico City. We ❤️ our fans, and your great city, and hope flying will soon be easier for us all.  We know we’re not the only ones experiencing this kind of flight trauma.

Just found out that this powerhouse @chorizomurray left this realm June 30th. We will never forget you; your talent, patience, intelligence and your smile. You were an incredible TM, sound engineer and friend. Thank you for that time in Bali, when we all had the honor to know your true spirit. Stunned. Heartbroken for her friends and family. Sending compassion to all experiencing this tragic loss. #teresamurray thank you @richardvelzenviii for this great shot.
